headline: ONEOK (OKE) Valuation Check as Short Interest Rises and Cramer Backs the Stock
summary: Short Interest Jumps as Cramer Throws Support Behind ONEOK ONEOK (OKE) just found itself in the crosshairs of both skeptics and fans, with short interest climbing while Jim Cramer publicly backed the stock for its natural gas pipeline footprint and dividend.
